Drinks were not refilled.
I just needed to get out of there and get a real meal.
The wallpaper was lifting from the wall, the place just felt dingy, the music coming in from the Casino was Loud and annoying.
I'd put my money that this place will be gone by the end of the year since it's one of those Once and Never again places.
I just wish I would have read the reviews on Yelp first.

